.Dd $Mdocdate: May 15 2015 $
.Dt FILTER-MONKEY 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm filter-monkey
.Nd smtpd filter to arbitrary reject mails
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
is a filter for
.Xr smtpd 8
which can be used to arbitrary filter mails.
Mails are randomly accepted with a probability of 70%, otherwise they
are rejected.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr filter_api 3 ,
.Xr smtpd.conf 5 ,
.Xr smtpd 8
.Sh HISTORY
The first version of
.Nm
was written in 2013.
